divs: Sighting DetailsWalking the dog at 1030 pm in a westerly direction along orchard ave 4 blockseast of lexington. In the SE sky I noticed motion and turned to look. I saw whatseemed to by a rather low flying source of withe light. It continued on in anorth easterly direction until out of sight. No sound.
